      • AnonymousEvent

        public AnonymousEvent(int type)
        Parameters:
        type - integer code for the json_event type. The sdk defines a few basics types DEFAULT_TYPE = 0; PAGED_PUBLICATION_OPENED = 1; PAGED_PUBLICATION_PAGE_DISAPPEARED = 2; OFFER_OPENED = 3; CLIENT_SESSION_OPENED = 4; SEARCHED = 5;
